doctype html
#clean-code.tab-pane.fade.in.active.col-lg-12
	.row
		.col-lg-6.col-md-6.animated.fadeInLeft
			img(src="bower_components/ultima/img/features/1.png", alt="Clean Code")
		.col-lg-6.col-md-6.animated.fadeInRight
			.row
				.col-lg-12(ng-controller="DomainAddCtrl")
					h2 Add New Domain

					p Start using deSEC for your Domain.
					p(ng-show="state==3") There was a problem with the server. Please check your input.
					form.form-inline(role="form",name="domainaddform",novalidate,ng-show="state==0")
						.form-group
							.input-group
								input(type="text",ng-model="domainname",required,placeholder="Domain Name")
						button.btn.btn-default(ng-click="domainadd(domainname)") Add
					p(ng-show="state==2")
						b {{ domain.name }} 
						| is ready to use with dane! 
						a(ng-click="state=0",href) Add more
					
					p.double-space-bottom
						| Using deSEC for your domains gives you awesome benefits, such as:
			.row
				.col-lg-2
					i.feature-icon.icon-support
				.col-lg-10(ng-controller="DomainTestCtrl")
					p
						| Paying money to our startup.
						
			.row
				.col-lg-2
					i.feature-icon.icon-map
				.col-lg-10
					p.double-space-bottom
						| Ending up on the terrorist watchlist.
			.row
				.col-lg-2
					i.feature-icon.icon-gift
				.col-lg-10
					p
						| Complicating your server setup.
			
